ProMED-mail <promed@promedmail.org>

[This report indicates that, in deprived communities lacking medical and
basic supportive care, mortality from measles virus infection can be very
high in young children; perhaps around 40 per cent in this case.

The HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map of Somaila can be accessed at:
